<p><b>Can anyone be a girlboss?</b> There are no set rules to becoming a Girl Boss, but the one thing they all have in common is ambition. Whether raising a family, building a business ground up, or striving in the workplace, Girl Bosses have a clear vision for their ambitions and do everything to achieve the ultimate goal.</p>
